{"tid":2038630,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人 反省","createTime":"2020-05-27T16:14:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T05:39:25.000Z","uid":328924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"12f3847525793949bcb3361242c5dff98b58ecbf","tid":2038630,"uid":328924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T16:14:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">其實大部分香港人根本未覺醒 我唔係想發放負能量 亦都唔係想話放棄同分化 但我地必須認清事實 政權嘅打壓只會越嚟越大 越嚟越冇底線同人性 手段亦都會非常狠毒 大家有目共睹</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果到今時今日我地仲係同一年前一樣 革命定必失敗告終 香港人必定要武裝自己嘅思想 我地呢一刻唔再向政權提出訴求 呢一刻 我地必須要奪權 脱離中共港共嘅操控 親手攞返屬於我地嘅權力同地方 我地要達到呢一個理想 <strong>必須反省 繼而進化</strong> 建立自己嘅革命意識民族意識 最後暴政必亡</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">香港獨立 <br />\n香港人 建國</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/448HqTC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F448HqTC.jpg&h=cf8d7b4c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f13c172831680323480f3bb6827e8bf1022c6b8","tid":2038630,"uid":328924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T16:17:29.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c9c1f6e9279d896e04258d3b61cd82ce0cc68d5","tid":2038630,"uid":328924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T16:17:52.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3b7792819ff65c4725af1f411e28b40e3cb89b8","tid":2038630,"uid":328924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T16:18:03.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70cbad17a93e204de86cd737fa7f85ac2adb86cf","tid":2038630,"uid":328924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T16:28:38.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a12f5b81aea367a7ba1dc21191e1dd948bb28849","tid":2038630,"uid":328924,"like":0,"dis